data.description: RESORT STYLE LIVING IN THE DESIRABLE COMMUNITY OF MANISTEE RANCH! This gorgeous home is located next to the large green belt and play area that traverses through the community. Large array of OWNED SOLAR PANELS COME FREE with this home! This popular & spacious floor plan includes a large bedroom & full bath downstairs. Main bedroom and 3 additional bedrooms & 2 full baths upstairs. Separate formal dining/living room. Large, covered patio with built-in outdoor kitchen for entertaining family & friends. Large backyard with pool, pavers, landscaping, and side area w/RV gate for additional storage/work shed, RV/Boat, or play uses. Beautiful views of the neighboring greenbelt w/walking/bike paths lined w/mature trees.  Seller is moving out of state & has priced this home for a quick sale!!
